Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:49.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just because you couldn't get a customer, you didn't have to drink so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:51.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.56,0:01:55.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A service much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're such a reliable little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:01:59.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Judy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.84,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Judy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:48.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:13.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this where Judy Devens died?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:21.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone called you Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard about it from Judy's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:27.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're the one who has been killing gang members all over America.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:31.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you're a real assassin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're an assassin, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.20,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Assassin, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:40.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:52.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please kill everyone with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:57.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The people who were there in the alley yesterday, the ones who fired guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and those who were supposed to receive this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:05.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kill everyone who killed Judy without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:09.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:24.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Judy, I'm Phantom's acquaintance now. {fnordtl}{}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:28.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He will definitely slay your killer... {fnordtl}{}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...with those five million dollars. {fnordtl}{}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Five million dollars isn't enough, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, the rest of the payment isn't much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can earn it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:59.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be my assistant for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:03.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:07.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}does being your assistant mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:11.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I can watch when we avenge Judy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:15.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But before that happens, there's something you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:20.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:22.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:33.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just pick the one you want the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:38.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I want all the clothes here equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:42.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I were to choose one, I would have to discard the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:53.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We won't do this only once in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you want something else as well,\N I'll take you here some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:56.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So just choose what you want to wear today for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:03.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umm, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hey. Is it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does it look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:15.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the first time I've worn such light and smooth clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After I finish cleaning up, I'll start cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because this place is dirty as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An assassin who cleans up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:44.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...sounds ridiculous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave the chores to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:55.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to earn what's not covered by the five million, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Say, Reiji. Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:10.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:13.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:14.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:14.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:17.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:19.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have your parents passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:25.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I ran away from the worst father there ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Judy found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:32.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If she hadn't, I'd probably be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that's why you said you're her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She was the only family I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:41.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But now she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:55.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do now that Judy is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:06.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even death comes in many forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:26.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, hold out your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Today's reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll cherish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:04.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll cherish it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All the actors have assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Playing her petty tricks, Claudia tried to manipulate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:18.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and now crafts yet another scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:23.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Her partner in crime is Godou Daisuke,\Nseeking to encroach upon Inferno's top echelons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:30.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wisemel unearthed the conspiracy and is trying to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:33.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A new actress has entered as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:37.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will create the grandest stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It will get hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:11.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is he Judy's killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:18.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At the very least, his organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's someone behind the water tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't, Mr. Godou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:18.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:42.64,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:51.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:55.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you get hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:00.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:16.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just wanted to confirm his identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You did great, spotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He was Judy's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've had your revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:38.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:43.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Move to route C and await further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:52.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, I heard a rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...saying that Isaac of the Bloodies died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:10.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then it's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:17.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.64,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Training me into an assassin, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:29.62,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it's fine with you, can I help with other assassinations too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:34.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The killing... is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:38.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.21,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'm just a nuisance now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:49.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I do have need of your cooking skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can be a cooking maid for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:54.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:57.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yahoo, I get to be a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've always wanted to try being a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maid uniforms are soo cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:22.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:29.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I... want to be your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:38.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your feelings about not letting me be an assassin, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:42.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You understand the sorrow of being an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:47.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, you have so many paths you can walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:49.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can be anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:52.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why must you become an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji, do you hate being an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:55.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:59.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, do you hate yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:05.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I became a killer and can't stop being a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:08.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm already broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you want to be like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I'm sorry, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I told the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know how many have died because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I were not in this world, they would be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:55.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They could return to their lovers and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:04.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you hadn't killed, someone else would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:11.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, do you wish to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you kill because you wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you like to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:21.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're different, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:25.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, Cal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:29.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}once you kill someone, the entire world changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even the sceneries you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and the sounds that reach your ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.45,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The way you are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:42.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't be able to accept kindness any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:44.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want you to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This place was not meant for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:52.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You shouldn't come over to my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you will always stay in that world, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:04.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I step into your world, I can be beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to stay beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be useful for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:23.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:28.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...wanted to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:45.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I could be with you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:46.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will come to your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to Cal's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:09.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:13.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Definitely, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:25.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A job at such a late hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I might be back late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go to sleep without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:32.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll stay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I picked up an old video recorder this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to see if I can repair it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You could just buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:43.97,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's a waste of money, the recorder might still be usable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Still usable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:48.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hope you return soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:54.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a promise then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a promise then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hooray, it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is the video rental store still open this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:46.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:53.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, Reiji is... Reiji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:12.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will come back, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You promised, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:06.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said you would never leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:10.06,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said we would be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:13.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He is a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:16.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were being tricked the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:23.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:25.97,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:37.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In these times, you can cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:43.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now we can be like in the days of old.
